            <div class="fyb-recipe-steps">
              <div class="fyb-col-label">Steps</div>
              <ol>
                <li>Grill + oven 425°F. Season chicken. Toss broccoli with EVOO + seasonings.</li>
                <li>Grill chicken ~18 min (flip once) to 165°F.</li>
                <li>Roast broccoli 22 min at 425°F; add cheese + crumbs, 2 min more. (Alt: air-fry 390°F, 6 min.)</li>
                <li>Air-fry fries 400°F, 10–12 min, shake halfway.</li>
              </ol>
