                <li>1.5 lbs beef stew meat, cubed</li>
                <li>Pearl barley (¾ cup), carrots, celery, onion</li>
                <li>Mushrooms, garlic, diced tomatoes (1 can)</li>
                <li>Beef broth (4 cups), Worcestershire, tomato paste</li>
                <li>Thyme, rosemary, bay leaf, salt/pepper, EVOO</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="fyb-recipe-steps">
              <div class="fyb-col-label">Steps</div>
