                <li>Season and sear beef in EVOO until browned on all sides; set aside.</li>
                <li>Sauté onion, carrots, celery 5 min. Add garlic + tomato paste 1 min.</li>
                <li>Return beef; add broth, tomatoes, barley, Worcestershire, herbs. Bring to boil.</li>
